{"tid":319665,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警車上遭受查人踢傷面    警員告一哥及施襲者","createTime":"2017-07-13T03:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T08:39:26.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f77473458b15c7c6e52e2b9c0f6a91de0dacc19a","tid":319665,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170713/large/1499916096_ab94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170713%2Flarge%2F1499916096_ab94.jpg&h=11e48096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名警員於2014年7月13日在中環德己立街執勤期間，疑在警車上遭受查者踢傷面部。事隔3年，該名警員入稟區域法院，向涉案男子和警務處處長索償，但未提及索償金額。<br />\n<br />\n原告張悅海，被告蔡偉鴻及警務處處長。入稟狀指，案發當日凌晨4時許，原告於停泊在德己立街的一輛警車上工作期間，因蔡不合法及蓄意的襲擊，以及警務處處長或其僱員的疏忽或違反僱傭合約責任，導致身體受傷，故興訟索償。"},{"pid":"96be9e5f68300ef1515c0bffa8e86d670117c831","tid":319665,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f0d8d28f7955528e39ade81451a197fe5f15bae","tid":319665,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n你打市民又要香港人比錢<br />\n你比市民打又要香港人比錢<br />\n有咩工好得過佢？"},{"pid":"fc0a46f43534eb90b0ea558ea140f5baf51789d1","tid":319665,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:08:00.000Z","msg":"點解唔係向施襲者索償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da3754a4c1bc889a7c403472fb27ee37575448f","tid":319665,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔係向施襲者索償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地冇錢話索條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21408d53ee8a6f3a5b6b61f6e7f04ae1df8275c1","tid":319665,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:39:26.00